{"type": "article", "id": 20478, "title": "你以为地产公司宣传册都是很恶俗的土豪画风吗？", "description": "通过这本书，你可以了解不少英国的设计很厉害的当代住宅——来自一个地产中介的总结。", "date": "2016-01-11T08:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 21829, "name": "当代住宅"}, {"id": 21830, "name": "The Modern House"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 135, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120859KIPrbClY1gu7kMx8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t最近，为庆祝公司成立十周年，英国的一家地产中介公司<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/the-modern-house-offers-great-architectural-escapes-to-those-who-need-to-get-away-from-it-all?iid=sr-link3\"> The Modern\r\nHouse</a> 出版了一本书，这是一本图册，集合了一些不错的地产项目。<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/the-modern-house-offers-great-architectural-escapes-to-those-who-need-to-get-away-from-it-all?iid=sr-link3\">The Modern\r\nHouse</a> 创建于 2005 年，由建筑师 Albert Hill 和记者 Matt Gibberd 共同成立，它主要从事房屋的买卖代理、中介出租工作。这本书则由出版社 Artifice Books 出版，售价约 30 欧元（约合 220 元人民币）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t地产商出书没啥稀奇的，但<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/britains-finest-modernist-homes-the-modern-house-book#141104\" target=\"_blank\">这本书的排版低调典雅，与花花绿绿、缺乏审美的地产宣传册形成了对比。</a>书籍主要分为四个章节：城市住宅、城市公寓、乡间别墅和多功能住宅，呈现了一些当代名建筑师作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212084895Duc0fKFOmzCVjy.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Manor Way, 设计师是 Peter Foggo 和 David Thomas, 1962\" alt=\"Manor Way, 设计师是 Peter Foggo 和 David Thomas, 1962\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Manor Way, 设计师是 Peter Foggo 和 David Thomas, 1962</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120849Zo90udFhMxwGNVyb.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Manor Way 的房间内部，这是室内餐厅\" alt=\"Manor Way 的房间内部，这是室内餐厅\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Manor Way 的房间内部，这是餐厅，屋内光线充分</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120849KVxE8CGIoYNZHqlW.jpg\" width=\"988\" height=\"944\" title=\"Barbican Estate, by Chamberlin, Powell and Bon, 1975 \" alt=\"Barbican Estate, by Chamberlin, Powell and Bon, 1975 \" data-ratio=\"0.95546559\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Barbican Estate, by Chamberlin, Powell and Bon, 1975 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120850TGVuOvc3JFCKZUSR.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"763\" title=\"Roof Garden Apartment, 设计者是 Richard Rogers 和 Tonkin Liu, 2002. \" alt=\"Roof Garden Apartment, 设计者是 Richard Rogers 和 Tonkin Liu, 2002. \" data-ratio=\"0.79479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Roof Garden Apartment, 设计者是 Richard Rogers 和 Tonkin Liu, 2002. </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120850nIkE5Qq6PHBshzwb.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Slip House, 设计者是 Carl Turner Architects, 2012 \" alt=\"Slip House, 设计者是 Carl Turner Architects, 2012 \" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Slip House, 设计者是 Carl Turner Architects, 2012 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120850VQs3oAaCXzBWgL2K.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"Inside Slip House\" alt=\"Inside Slip House\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> Slip House 内部，极简的空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120851vPCJiOcfhzwA9NYg.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"The Walled Garden, 设计者是 Michael Manser, 2002 \" alt=\"The Walled Garden, 设计者是 Michael Manser, 2002 \" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>The Walled Garden, 设计者是 Michael Manser, 2002</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120853SkXz2ls7bDNRpH68.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Ahm House, 设计者是 Jørn Utzon 和 Povl Ahm, 1962 \" alt=\"Ahm House, 设计者是 Jørn Utzon 和 Povl Ahm, 1962 \" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Ahm House, 设计者是 Jørn Utzon 和 Povl Ahm, 1962</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120853pVgcnyDNZUQwujlT.jpg\" width=\"629\" height=\"944\" title=\"Ahm House 的另一个角度\" alt=\"Ahm House 的另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"1.50079491\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Ahm House 的另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120854buRD4w8yTKpsc9NA.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Red Bridge House, 设计者是 Piers Smerin, 2013 \" alt=\"Red Bridge House, 设计者是 Piers Smerin, 2013 \" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Red Bridge House, 设计者是 Piers Smerin, 2013</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120854T0R3ZS7ePdBjVsHo.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"669\" title=\" 6a Architects 的一处作品\" alt=\" 6a Architects 的一处作品\" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> 6a Architects 的一处作品</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120855y9gCnbi5cWPsm7z4.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"这处房子的设计者则是 Zoe Chan 和 Merlin Ears ，它竣工于 2014 年\" alt=\"这处房子的设计者则是 Zoe Chan 和 Merlin Ears ，它竣工于 2014 年\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这处房子的设计者则是 Zoe Chan 和 Merlin Ears ，它竣工于 2014 年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120855SjIKG6ZkXJOEH4RL.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"这是房子内部充满个性的台阶\" alt=\"这是房子内部充满个性的台阶\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这是房子内部充满个性的台阶</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120856ruFLDUwA2Zcas4g7.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"House in Highgate Cemetery, 设计者是 Eldridge Smerin, 2008. \" alt=\"House in Highgate Cemetery, 设计者是 Eldridge Smerin, 2008. \" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>House in Highgate Cemetery, 设计者是 Eldridge Smerin, 2008.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021208569ikIZqwRdPsV23jb.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"588\" title=\"Lost House, 设计者是 Adjaye Associates, 2003.\" alt=\"Lost House, 设计者是 Adjaye Associates, 2003.\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Lost House, 设计者是 Adjaye Associates, 2003.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t目前，The Modern House 主要从事房屋买卖、招租等业务，在网站上，可以看到创始人的照片：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120857Hb4e1X6ykWDzTtBp.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"532\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.55416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t下面则是他们经营的房子了：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021208579sC6LpjM5nqfKIAw.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"556\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.57916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021208584Pvk8TcaKhI1tgbi.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"557\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.58020833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120858na35YiHwksg6tuMz.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"563\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.58645833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/britains-finest-modernist-homes-the-modern-house-book#141104\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}